     H            Y.
     F** VVVRA1 ****************************
     F* CREATE PF-LF TABLE                 *
     F**************************************
     FVVVWPA1 IF  E                    DISK
     FVVVPPA1 O   E                    DISK                      A
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  10 WHRFI
     I                                        4   5 KBN
      *
     C                     READ VVVWPA1                  81
     C           *IN81     DOWEQ'0'
     C           WHRTYP    IFEQ 'P'
     C                     EXSR #SB001
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     READ VVVWPA1                  81
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                                         *
      *-----------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB001    BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVELWHRFI     VVRFI
     C                     MOVELWHREFI    VVREFI
     C                     WRITEVVVPPA11
      *
     CSR         ESB001    ENDSR
